5|$|<b>I</b> <b>beg</b> {{to tender}} the {{following}} suggestion {{as a means}} of getting over the difficulty: that ten or twelve of the most prominent clubs in England combine to arrange home-and-away fixtures each season, the said fixtures to be arranged at a friendly conference {{about the same time as}} the International Conference.|$|E
5|$|The story I {{am going}} to tell is a horrible one: <b>I</b> <b>beg</b> that daughters and fathers should hold {{themselves}} aloof, while I sing, or if they find my songs enchanting, let them refuse to believe this part of my tale, and suppose that it never happened: or else, if they believe that it did happen, they must believe also in the punishment that followed.|$|E
